  ID: MalteseSoldier2
  Name: Matteo, Italian crossbowman
  Icon: {fileID: 409668665, guid: 4147f2bc6fccc974f937adc9cd1a5700, type: 3}
  Description: "He earns his living as a fletcher in peacetime and tells everyone
    that wood obeys him. A collapsing merlon slammed his forearm and bent bone like
    green timber; now he can\u2019t clench a fist.\n\nTreatment: Leather strap becomes
    a crude tourniquet to control swelling. You probe but find no single extraction
    point \u2014 just a smashed limb. Splint it to stop wandering bone. Hope circulation
    survives.\n\nRequires: 1 Bandage"
